The paper discusses the security and privacy issues of IoT devices, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of sensors in IoT devices, which can be related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also discusses countermeasures to secure the sensors of IoT devices, which can be related to software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper discusses the future research directions, which can be related to networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
